wikipedia_page.main: Lieutenant General Sir Benjamin John Bathurst  (born 15 April 1964) is a senior British Army officer.

response: *Sir Benjamin Bathurst (courtier) (c. 1639–1704), MP for Bere Alston & New Romney, Cofferer of the Household, British East India Company's governor
